mponents that drive them.The next session will be held Dec. 3, at 11 a.m. CT.  ...    Stay tuned for a Markets+ Congestion Rent podcast being released in September on the SPP Learning Center! As the first  ...    On-Demand Self-Study Courses Explore self-paced courses in theLearning Centerthat cover Integrated Marketplace concepts, which can provide understanding of SPP’s market design, the foundation for Markets+. Log into yourSPP Learning Centeraccount to register for upcoming training, self-study courses, access  ...    |\n|\n|\n|\n|\nSept. 11\n|\nJoint MSWG/MRATF Net Conference\n|\nSept. 11\n|  ...    Facebook|Share This Email|  ...    LinkedIn|Share This Email|\n|\n| FacebookXLinkedIn|\n|\n| SPP|Contact Us|Privacy Policy\n|\n|\n|\n|\n| Southwest Power Pool |201 Worthen Drive|Little Rock, AR 72223 US\n|\n|\n|\n|\n| Unsubscribe|Update Profile|Constant Contact Data Notice\n|\n|\n|"
