en by input from committees and working groups. READ MORE\n\n### Markets+ State Committee (MSC) MSC was established to ensure each state's interests are well-represented as Markets+ is further developed and  ...    READ MORE\n\n### Markets+ Participants Executive Committee (MPEC) MPEC is responsible for advancing policies and procedures for technical operations to the Markets+ Independent Panel. READ MORE\n\nVIEW WORKING GROUPS\n\n# Timeline SPP has made a long-term commitment to secure cost-effective, reliable and diverse energy for Markets+ participants. # Contact Us Have questions about Markets+? Reach out to us and we'll connect you with the right individual or working group. CONTACT US"
